.TH "evergreen_page_flip" 9 "evergreen_page_flip" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
evergreen_page_flip \- pageflip callback.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" evergreen_page_flip
.BI "(struct radeon_device *rdev "  ","
.BI "int crtc_id "  ","
.BI "u64 crtc_base "  ","
.BI "bool async "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rdev" 12
radeon_device pointer
.IP "crtc_id" 12
crtc to cleanup pageflip on
.IP "crtc_base" 12
new address of the crtc (GPU MC address)
.IP "async" 12
asynchronous flip
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Triggers the actual pageflip by updating the primary
surface base address (evergreen+).
